Package: theharvester
Version: 4.10.1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: proot, tar, axel, nethunter-cli
Section: recon
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/laramies/theHarvester
Description: E-mail, Subdomain, and Name Harvester
 theHarvester is a tool for gathering e-mails, subdomains, hosts,
 employee names, open ports and banners from different public sources
 like search engines, PGP key servers, and SHODAN database.
